history.content:
To increase units beyond 20.5, CS-intended/undeclared students should meet with an L&S Advisor.

Declared CS students, fill out this form. We will review and notify you at the beginning of the 3rd week of the semester. Please plan accordingly.

EECS Students, meet with your ESS Advisor to discuss their process.
